---
title: "How to automatically convert TikZ images to SVG with Quarto"
date: 2026-02-25
description: "Make Quarto convert TikZ graphics to SVG files when rendering to non-LaTeX outputs like HTML, Word, and Typst"

image: "fancy-dag.png"
twitter-card:
  image: "fancy-dag.png"
open-graph:
  image: "fancy-dag.png"

categories:
  - quarto
